{
  "episode_id": "2026-07-11",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友们大家好啊，欢迎收听AI每日先锋，今天是2026年7月11日，我是苏晴。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 6.618,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，我是周航。",
      "start": 8.067,
      "duration": 1.698,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "周航，你今天早上刷新闻了没？OpenAI那边动静可太大了。",
      "start": 10.262,
      "duration": 7.314,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "怎么没刷，我盯着发布会看了一个多小时。说实话，手心一直在出汗。",
      "start": 18.029,
      "duration": 5.573,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我跟你说，GPT-5这名字一出来，朋友圈直接刷屏了。但我发现好多人其实就转发个标题，根本说不清它到底牛在哪。",
      "start": 24.007,
      "duration": 8.751,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这就是我想聊的。你注意啊，GPT-5这次的核心变化不在参数堆砌，而是它处理复杂任务的方式。以前大模型更像是一个聊天工具，现在它开始像一个能自己规划步骤、调用工具、跑完全流程的\"思考者\"了。",
      "start": 33.191,
      "duration": 19.045,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你这么一说我就有画面了。就好比以前点外卖要自己选店、选菜、下单，现在它帮你整套流程跑完，是不是这意思？",
      "start": 52.701,
      "duration": 9.012,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "差不多，而且它能跨应用去执行。说白了，你给它一个模糊的目标，它能自己拆解、自己干活、自己修正。这种能力上来之后，所有做Agent的创业公司都得掂量掂量，自己的护城河还剩多少。",
      "start": 62.175,
      "duration": 14.082,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这也太狠了。我突然想到一个事，那些基于GPT-4搭产品的公司，会不会一夜之间被淘汰？",
      "start": 76.708,
      "duration": 9.186,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "不会一夜归零，但洗牌是一定的。模型能力上了一个台阶，原来很多\"伪需求\"的解决方案瞬间变成真功能，原来\"真功能\"的方案又变得平庸。这就是为什么我说，所有定价策略都得重新来一遍。",
      "start": 86.394,
      "duration": 14.125,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "行，这个先记下。对了，有件事我觉得比GPT-5还刺激——苹果居然把OpenAI给告了。",
      "start": 100.957,
      "duration": 8.446,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你看，我第一反应也是翻诉状原文，看完心情挺复杂。这事儿确实离谱。",
      "start": 109.864,
      "duration": 5.878,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "怎么回事？苹果和OpenAI不是合作伙伴吗？iPhone里都集成ChatGPT了啊，怎么突然撕破脸？",
      "start": 116.187,
      "duration": 8.185,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这就是最有意思的地方。表面上看是商业秘密纠纷，苹果指控OpenAI一位前员工——也是现在OpenAI的关键人物——把苹果的核心技术带过去了。但往深了想，这案子其实是苹果对整个AI生态话语权的一次反击。",
      "start": 124.846,
      "duration": 17.086,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "等等我插一句，你说这位前员工，到底带走了啥？",
      "start": 142.359,
      "duration": 4.659,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "诉状里提到的是苹果内部用于训练和优化模型的关键技术与数据。这人长期在苹果负责这块，跳槽OpenAI之后直接参与了他们的核心模型研发。苹果的意思很明确——人可以走，技术与数据不能带走。",
      "start": 147.482,
      "duration": 18.523,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这么一听好像也有道理。但是不是也太巧了，正好赶上GPT-5发布这个节骨眼递诉状？",
      "start": 166.422,
      "duration": 9.535,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你注意这个时间点，确实耐人寻味。GPT-5一出整个行业都在讨论OpenAI有多强，苹果这时候告，未必全是\"秋后算账\"。更深层的信号是告诉市场：你们别以为OpenAI是白月光，它的技术底子也有来路不明的地方。",
      "start": 176.393,
      "duration": 18.087,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "懂了，这是商战里的舆论战。那你觉得这案子最后会怎么判？",
      "start": 194.897,
      "duration": 4.746,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "判什么不是关键，关键是这案子会逼着整个行业重新划线。以后AI公司之间的人才流动，特别是那些掌握核心机密的，怎么签竞业、怎么隔离数据，都得立新规矩。",
      "start": 200.139,
      "duration": 12.974,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我听完后背有点凉。感觉AI这行，表面是技术革命，背后全是刀光剑影。",
      "start": 213.525,
      "duration": 6.4,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "本来就是。不过话说回来，今天还有些消息也挺",
      "start": 220.404,
      "duration": 3.701,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好了听众朋友们，以上就是今天的AI每日先锋。感谢收听，我们明天见！",
      "start": 224.537,
      "duration": 6.879,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
